cSystemFont, &quot;avenir next&quot;, avenir, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, helvetica, Ubuntu, roboto, noto, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, ui-sans-serif, sans-serif; line-height: inherit; text-decoration-line: inherit; outline: 0px; list-style: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;Having access to digital learning modules in the classroom is a game-changer, allowing young students to access more information than ever before. With virtual simulations and models, teachers can communicate subjects that may have previously been out of reach. Similarly, video conferencing and social platforms allow students to communicate with others from different countries and share information like never before.&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; background: none transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; line-height: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; text-transform: inherit; outline: 0px; list-style: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border: 0px; white-space: initial;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 48px; color: rgb(17, 73, 84); background: none rgb(250, 242, 237); font-family: Obelisc, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;avenir next&quot;, avenir, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, helvetica, Ubuntu, roboto, noto, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, ui-sans-serif, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; text-decoration-line: inherit; outline: 0px; list-style: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 